月24日14時20分許 桃園市○○區○○路000 號之黑松公司中壢廠（未返回宏全公司） 蝴蝶籠58只。 (185,600元)","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHM/111%2c%e4%b8%8a%e6%98%93%2c27%2c20220414%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,111,上易,27,20220414,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"上易","JNO":"27","JDATE":"20220414","JTITLE":"詐欺"}